OL,7,FDuring a court hearing in Cardiff in
OL,8,FJanuary this year, the health board
OL,9,Fadmitted full liability for its
OL,10,Fneonatal care and for the injuries
OL,11,Fsuffered by Gethin, who now requires
OL,12,F24-hour specialist care.
OL,14,FSwansea Bay University Health Board
OL,15,Fsays it apologises to the Channons for
OL,16,Fthe trauma and life-changing impacts
OL,17,Ftheir failings have caused, as well as
OL,18,Ffor the time it took the health board
OL,19,Fto admit liability.
