OL,7,FAs a result of the report, the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment has escalated the Health
OL,9,FBoard's maternity and neonatal
OL,10,Fservices to the second-highest level
OL,11,Fof intervention - Level 4 - providing
OL,12,Fenhanced monitoring and support.
OL,14,FGethin's mother, Sian Channon, told
OL,15,FITV News, "It doesn't end because we
OL,16,Fhave had an admission. For Gethin, he
OL,17,Fis still left with devastating
OL,18,Finjuries, and as a family, we have
OL,19,Fbeen crushed by what has happened to
OL,20,Fhim. It's been a fight that's been
OL,21,Fexhausting and long-lived".
