OL,7,FThe Channon family say they were first
OL,8,Falerted to the possibility that
OL,9,FGethin's treatment contributed to his
OL,10,Finjuries when a report by one of the
OL,11,FUK's top maternity investigators, Dr
OL,12,FBill Kirkup, uncovered several
OL,13,Ffailures in Gethin's care.
