OL,7,F"We've come a long way from being told
OL,8,Fthat what happened to Gethin was just
OL,9,Fone of those things," Robert Channon
OL,10,Ftold ITV News.
OL,12,F"From them challenging the letter and
OL,13,Freport from Dr Bill Kirkup, and the
OL,14,Fhostility that we faced and the
OL,15,Fmultiple health board denials in
OL,16,Fpublic or media statements or board
OL,17,Fminutes, we should never have been put
OL,18,Fin that position when we were only
OL,19,Ffighting to get answers to what
OL,20,Fhappened to our son."
