OL,7,FA Swansea Bay University health Board
OL,8,Fspokesperson said:"We wrote to Mr and
OL,9,FMrs Channon on 21 October 2024
OL,10,Ffollowing an external review, which we
OL,11,Fhad commissioned to look into the care
OL,12,Fwe provided. That letter provided an
OL,13,Funreserved and heartfelt apology and
OL,14,Faccepted liability on behalf of the
OL,15,Fhealth board for failings related to
OL,16,Fthe care of their son following his
OL,17,Fbirth.
