OL,7,F"We have not commented on this
OL,8,Fpublicly following the family's own
OL,9,Frequest to us last year for us to
OL,10,Fmaintain confidentiality. However, as
OL,11,Fthe family has now raised this
OL,12,Fpublicly, we are now able to comment
OL,13,Fand would like to take the opportunity
OL,14,Fto reiterate the apology we made at
OL,15,Fthe time, but this time in public, for
OL,16,Fthe trauma and life-changing impacts
OL,17,Fthat our failings have caused. We are
OL,18,Falso sorry for how long it took to
OL,19,Fcome to a conclusion regarding our
OL,20,Fliability."
